  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to evaluate risk factors and complications of ventral hernia repair.
      A retrospective study of journal files with patients undergoing ventral hernia repair, and an
      analyses of complications by use of the Clavien-Dindo classification of surgical
      complications.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
